1
00:00:02,340 --> 00:00:03,360
Aren't we

2
00:00:03,860 --> 00:00:05,610
supposed to be working?

3
00:00:05,640 --> 00:00:06,840
Why are you...

4
00:00:07,910 --> 00:00:09,560
putting me in a cosplay costume?

5
00:00:10,540 --> 00:00:12,560
You agreed to work with me, right?

6
00:00:14,100 --> 00:00:15,520
Try to understand my world.

7
00:00:16,840 --> 00:00:18,560
I've seen a lot from your world already,

8
00:00:19,520 --> 00:00:20,560
the dance movements

9
00:00:21,060 --> 00:00:22,360
and Khon terms.

10
00:00:24,340 --> 00:00:26,640
But I never asked to be Hanuman.

11
00:00:27,880 --> 00:00:28,800
Good.

12
00:00:29,080 --> 00:00:30,120
You don't have the face for it.

13
00:00:48,320 --> 00:00:49,000
Hey!

14
00:00:51,160 --> 00:00:52,880
What are you doing?

15
00:00:53,020 --> 00:00:54,880
Come on. Just try it out.

16
00:01:18,700 --> 00:01:19,760
Whoa!

17
00:01:20,280 --> 00:01:21,880
You totally killed it!

18
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:23,440
See?

19
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:25,600
But I'm not used to this.

20
00:01:27,500 --> 00:01:29,500
I'm not used to
your Thotsakan moves either.

21
00:01:31,140 --> 00:01:32,780
I'm trying to understand your world, too.

22
00:01:34,040 --> 00:01:35,880
That's because you want to be Thotsakan.

23
00:01:37,900 --> 00:01:39,400
And you want to work with me.

24
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:41,330
Try to understand my world, then.

25
00:01:46,340 --> 00:01:47,360
You're...

26
00:01:48,460 --> 00:01:49,360
quite a nutcase.

27
00:01:50,490 --> 00:01:53,320
I'm a nutcase who wants only
one million more views on Khon.

28
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:57,800
Alright, what are you teaching me today?

29
00:01:58,160 --> 00:01:59,200
I'm good to go.

30
00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:11,280
[Tanakorn Chuen-arom as Saen/Sand]

31
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:16,040
[Wacharathon Wongyai as Rak/Lucky]

32
00:02:16,420 --> 00:02:20,220
[Worachai Areewong as Tan/Thank]

33
00:02:20,580 --> 00:02:25,300
[Khitaphat Choothai as Chim/Charm]

34
00:02:25,500 --> 00:02:28,900
[Kornkamon Supaseripap as Vila/ViVi]

35
00:02:29,180 --> 00:02:33,160
[Rungtiva Sangngoen as Prink
Napat Seela as Rit/Ton]

36
00:02:33,340 --> 00:02:36,740
[Chalisa Schaub as Kamala
Weeraachai Hatgovit as Phraya Banleng]

37
00:02:36,900 --> 00:02:41,100
[Nithiroj Simakamtorn as Phraya Dechanarong
Rattanachai Phakdirat as Khon Master]

38
00:02:52,720 --> 00:02:54,720
Move this footage a bit to the left.

39
00:02:54,860 --> 00:02:56,850
- Ah!
- So it matches the sound.

40
00:02:56,880 --> 00:02:57,810
- Mhm.
- Okay, okay.

41
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:59,690
- Should we add some effects?
- So it'll stay the same.

42
00:02:59,720 --> 00:03:00,880
I think it'll be the same.

43
00:03:01,040 --> 00:03:02,810
You have to click here.

44
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:05,000
Really? Okay, let's try.

45
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:06,290
See?

46
00:03:06,320 --> 00:03:07,570
- Boom!
- Whoa!

47
00:03:07,600 --> 00:03:08,960
- Kidding.
- What the hell?

48
00:03:09,100 --> 00:03:11,130
- What was that?
- Right? What was that?

49
00:03:11,160 --> 00:03:13,190
Get excited, my friends. We have to

50
00:03:13,220 --> 00:03:14,610
- build up our energy.
- Mhm.

51
00:03:14,640 --> 00:03:15,480
Oh!

52
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:18,360
Come look at this.
It's almost done.

53
00:03:18,640 --> 00:03:20,250
- Come on, sit down.
- Let him have a look.

54
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,450
- Come here.
- Come on.

55
00:03:21,480 --> 00:03:22,680
Let him see it.

56
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:26,880
- So exciting!
- You can't leave.

57
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:28,290
That's quite a lot.

58
00:03:28,320 --> 00:03:29,530
- Quite a lot.
- Not enough for...

59
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:30,930
- About to run out.
- I think

60
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:32,680
- this is so cool.
- I'll eat it in a bit.

61
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:35,040
Let me.

62
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:37,320
I'm hungry, so what?

63
00:03:38,440 --> 00:03:40,800
- Wanna fix it?
- Can you move this one a bit?

64
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:42,000
Okay.

65
00:03:42,030 --> 00:03:43,630
- Let me try.
- Okay.

66
00:03:43,660 --> 00:03:46,320
Try to check it, alright?

67
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:49,400
You're right. That's better.

68
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:51,320
I think that'll work.

69
00:03:51,880 --> 00:03:53,360
It's so cool.

70
00:03:53,720 --> 00:03:54,560
That's fine.

71
00:03:54,920 --> 00:03:56,280
It's about to run out.

72
00:03:56,640 --> 00:03:58,330
- No. Leave it to me.
- The snacks, I mean.

73
00:03:58,360 --> 00:04:00,010
Guys, stop. Let me.

74
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:01,890
Let me.

75
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:03,650
- You're that hardworking?
- I'm hungry.

76
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:05,250
Guys, stop. Leave it to me.

77
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:06,900
- You're at it again.
- 'Cause I'm hungry.

78
00:04:07,820 --> 00:04:08,850
- Sand?
- Huh?

79
00:04:08,880 --> 00:04:09,640
I think...

80
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,690
just a little more

81
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:13,580
- should be enough.
- A little bit more.

82
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:15,800
Yeah, okay.

83
00:04:30,640 --> 00:04:31,550
You're feeding me?

84
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:42,040
I dropped it. Want it?

85
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:43,240
No, I'm good.

86
00:04:43,440 --> 00:04:44,440
Alright then.

87
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:54,880
Look.

88
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,120
Is this our clip?

89
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:58,200
- Whoa!
- What?

90
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:59,290
99...

91
00:04:59,320 --> 00:05:00,170
- What the...
- Whoa...

92
00:05:00,200 --> 00:05:00,890
Whoa!

93
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:01,970
- Shit!
- 99...

94
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:03,610
- One million views!!
- One million!!

95
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:05,650
- Whoa! Whoa!
- One million views!

96
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:07,230
- Whoa!
- One million!

97
00:05:07,260 --> 00:05:09,040
- One million views!
- How is this possible?

98
00:05:09,200 --> 00:05:10,610
- This is awesome!
- So cool!

99
00:05:10,640 --> 00:05:11,690
Amazing!

100
00:05:12,570 --> 00:05:14,020
Am I dreaming?

101
00:05:14,060 --> 00:05:15,800
- You're not.
- I told you we could do it.

102
00:05:15,830 --> 00:05:17,720
- Amazing!
- One million views!

103
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:19,240
How?!

104
00:05:19,440 --> 00:05:21,450
Good job! This is awesome!

105
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:22,410
Good job!

106
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:24,280
- One million views!
- Good job!

107
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:26,020
You're so cool.

108
00:05:26,380 --> 00:05:27,120
What's wrong?

109
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,400
What's the matter?

110
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:30,120
- Aren't you happy?
- Right?

111
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:31,960
I am...

112
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:33,780
It's just...

113
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:35,880
If my grandpa saw this,

114
00:05:37,200 --> 00:05:38,610
I don't know what he'd think.

115
00:05:38,640 --> 00:05:39,960
Hey!

116
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:41,600
Don't worry.

117
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:44,640
I think he'll understand.

118
00:05:44,880 --> 00:05:45,680
Yeah.

119
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:48,840
Hey, we didn't ruin it, did we?

120
00:05:49,300 --> 00:05:50,240
Mhm.

121
00:05:58,920 --> 00:06:00,370
Nice job!

122
00:06:00,400 --> 00:06:01,680
I'm so happy.

123
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:04,000
- How did we pull this off?
- I know right?

124
00:06:05,400 --> 00:06:06,240
Hello, Mom.

125
00:06:08,620 --> 00:06:09,480
I'm sorry?

126
00:06:12,280 --> 00:06:14,080
Grandpa wants to see me this evening?

127
00:06:21,140 --> 00:06:22,200
Okay.

128
00:06:37,740 --> 00:06:38,600
You...

129
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:40,200
Why are you here?

130
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:42,400
Well, I'm here to help you.

131
00:06:43,400 --> 00:06:44,640
It's my idea, after all.

132
00:06:46,080 --> 00:06:47,680
I can't let you take the blame alone.

133
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:52,160
But you seem more scared than me.

134
00:06:53,400 --> 00:06:54,520
Of course I am.

135
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,240
How could I not?

136
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:58,320
But

137
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:00,520
it's better than you facing it alone.

138
00:07:18,640 --> 00:07:19,760
- Good evening.
- Good evening.

139
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:26,320
This... This is Sand.

140
00:07:26,440 --> 00:07:27,550
He's from my Khon club.

141
00:07:27,580 --> 00:07:28,520
Good evening, sir.

142
00:07:36,640 --> 00:07:39,640
I saw your clip.

143
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:49,520
Well,

144
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:50,920
Grandpa,

145
00:07:51,340 --> 00:07:54,000
I just want younger generations

146
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:56,680
to see that Khon can be cool.

147
00:07:58,120 --> 00:07:59,880
I didn't mean to...

148
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,640
disrespect it.

149
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:05,600
Please don't be too hard on Lucky.

150
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:08,520
The clip was my idea.

151
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:10,480
So...

152
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,360
if you're going to scold him,

153
00:08:13,880 --> 00:08:14,880
please scold me instead.

154
00:08:23,540 --> 00:08:27,000
Why would I scold the two of you?

155
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:28,320
Hm?

156
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:33,280
What you did

157
00:08:33,740 --> 00:08:36,520
is a good way to expand the idea.

158
00:08:37,160 --> 00:08:38,240
Very good.

159
00:08:40,140 --> 00:08:40,920
But...

160
00:08:41,380 --> 00:08:42,960
you told me that

161
00:08:43,500 --> 00:08:46,400
Khon has a pattern to follow, didn't you?

162
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:51,280
Then why don't you call it a Ramakien show?

163
00:08:52,460 --> 00:08:54,600
It's true that Khon

164
00:08:55,040 --> 00:08:56,960
has its own patterns,

165
00:08:57,900 --> 00:08:59,530
but Ramakien

166
00:08:59,560 --> 00:09:01,960
doesn't always have to be Khon.

167
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:03,400
Isn't that right?

168
00:09:10,640 --> 00:09:11,880
Thank you, Grandpa.

169
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,960
I'm glad that you understand.

170
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:20,120
And this friend of yours...

171
00:09:21,680 --> 00:09:25,000
Are you the one
who gave my grandson the courage

172
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:27,160
to think outside the box?

173
00:09:27,860 --> 00:09:28,600
Well...

174
00:09:30,680 --> 00:09:33,040
I just encouraged him
to breathe freely in his own world.

175
00:09:39,340 --> 00:09:41,000
Good, very good.

176
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:43,160
Art

177
00:09:44,040 --> 00:09:46,720
must have both roots and branches,

178
00:09:47,060 --> 00:09:48,400
like what you did,

179
00:09:49,060 --> 00:09:50,800
so it can stand strong.

180
00:09:54,100 --> 00:09:55,760
Let's have dinner, shall we?

181
00:09:56,380 --> 00:09:57,440
I'm hungry.

182
00:09:58,640 --> 00:09:59,720
Join us, Sand.

183
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:01,920
Yes.

184
00:10:25,710 --> 00:10:27,350
I thought I'd get a ride home.

185
00:10:28,830 --> 00:10:30,430
Your house is very close.

186
00:10:30,510 --> 00:10:31,910
It's only a short walk.

187
00:10:33,250 --> 00:10:34,150
Well...

188
00:10:38,730 --> 00:10:40,190
Thank you, really.

189
00:10:41,910 --> 00:10:42,830
For what?

190
00:10:43,630 --> 00:10:44,750
I didn't do anything.

191
00:10:45,270 --> 00:10:45,990
Of course you did.

192
00:10:47,950 --> 00:10:48,990
You made me

193
00:10:49,510 --> 00:10:51,030
see Khon in a different light.

194
00:10:53,590 --> 00:10:55,030
I used to think that

195
00:10:55,390 --> 00:10:56,710
tradition was a sacred thing

196
00:10:57,850 --> 00:10:58,750
and couldn't be touched.

197
00:11:00,950 --> 00:11:02,150
But now I understand

198
00:11:04,250 --> 00:11:05,510
that certain things

199
00:11:06,430 --> 00:11:07,670
live on

200
00:11:10,570 --> 00:11:11,750
because they dare to change.

201
00:11:18,190 --> 00:11:20,640
And certain things won't disappear

202
00:11:23,630 --> 00:11:25,510
if someone like you preserves them.

203
00:11:31,190 --> 00:11:34,030
But preserving something
doesn't mean constantly scolding.

204
00:11:45,750 --> 00:11:46,550
Get home safe.

205
00:11:49,810 --> 00:11:50,510
Hey,

206
00:11:51,150 --> 00:11:51,830
Sand.

207
00:11:54,690 --> 00:11:55,310
Hmm?

208
00:11:56,710 --> 00:11:57,630
Well,

209
00:11:58,390 --> 00:11:59,670
I'm not sure

210
00:12:01,390 --> 00:12:03,190
if you're still mad at me,

211
00:12:06,110 --> 00:12:07,430
but I'm not mad at you anymore.

212
00:12:08,830 --> 00:12:09,990
And...

213
00:12:11,670 --> 00:12:13,310
I'd love to be with you,

214
00:12:15,470 --> 00:12:16,870
not only at the club.

215
00:12:20,270 --> 00:12:21,750
I'm not mad at you anymore.

216
00:12:24,750 --> 00:12:26,150
Just don't give up on teaching me.

217
00:12:30,730 --> 00:12:31,870
I'll be with you like this

218
00:12:32,990 --> 00:12:33,830
always.

219
00:12:41,610 --> 00:12:42,310
Deal.

220
00:12:52,430 --> 00:12:53,870
Should I die and be reborn,

221
00:12:55,230 --> 00:12:56,750
were we to dance Khon together once more,

222
00:12:58,470 --> 00:13:00,070
I would feel little sorrow.

223
00:13:17,110 --> 00:13:18,390
What devilry is this?!

224
00:13:19,830 --> 00:13:21,350
You! And him!

225
00:13:21,860 --> 00:13:23,790
Are you engaged
in an illicit affair with a servant?!

226
00:13:27,630 --> 00:13:28,390
Father...

227
00:13:28,420 --> 00:13:29,140
Silence!

228
00:13:30,070 --> 00:13:32,190
Do not dare call yourself my son!

229
00:13:33,470 --> 00:13:36,630
Are you heaping more shame upon me,
beyond what Rit has already done?!

230
00:13:38,470 --> 00:13:40,390
Not only is your affair with a servant,

231
00:13:40,810 --> 00:13:42,790
but he is a man!!

232
00:13:43,770 --> 00:13:46,590
There is nothing more abhorrent than this!!

233
00:13:51,870 --> 00:13:53,630
Pray, lay no blame upon Master Rak,
Your Excellency.

234
00:13:56,810 --> 00:13:57,510
All of this

235
00:13:58,230 --> 00:13:59,910
is mine alone to bear.

236
00:14:01,050 --> 00:14:02,390
Yet I must assure you,

237
00:14:03,730 --> 00:14:06,230
I mean no harm nor deceit.

238
00:14:09,670 --> 00:14:11,030
My heart holds nothing...

239
00:14:12,910 --> 00:14:14,470
save the love I bear Master Rak.

240
00:14:15,030 --> 00:14:16,010
Love, you say?!

241
00:14:17,270 --> 00:14:20,150
Your love has brought my son to ruin,

242
00:14:20,870 --> 00:14:21,900
and shame

243
00:14:21,930 --> 00:14:23,070
and disgrace upon the family!!

244
00:14:23,670 --> 00:14:24,710
Father!

245
00:14:25,250 --> 00:14:27,350
Pray, do not harm him.

246
00:14:29,670 --> 00:14:32,270
I bear the burden of two wretched sons.

247
00:14:33,270 --> 00:14:35,030
You are but like your brother.

248
00:14:35,470 --> 00:14:37,510
You have shamed me!

249
00:14:39,170 --> 00:14:39,990
All of you!

250
00:14:40,830 --> 00:14:41,750
Seize him at once!

251
00:14:41,950 --> 00:14:43,590
Bring me a whip!!

252
00:14:46,430 --> 00:14:47,550
- Saen...
- Master Rak...

253
00:14:48,430 --> 00:14:49,230
Saen!

254
00:15:02,550 --> 00:15:03,390
Unhand me!

255
00:15:04,470 --> 00:15:05,350
Unhand me!!

256
00:15:10,350 --> 00:15:12,150
I beg you, Father, spare him.

257
00:15:13,390 --> 00:15:14,650
Pray, do not harm him.

258
00:15:16,230 --> 00:15:17,350
I beg of you.

259
00:15:18,710 --> 00:15:20,150
Do not bid me what I must do!

260
00:15:20,830 --> 00:15:23,310
The wretch who has brought shame
upon my family

261
00:15:23,670 --> 00:15:26,070
shall suffer for his deeds!

262
00:15:27,190 --> 00:15:28,030
My dear!

263
00:15:28,750 --> 00:15:30,150
What disturbance is this?

264
00:15:31,730 --> 00:15:33,750
Your wicked son

265
00:15:34,410 --> 00:15:37,550
has committed fornication
with a male servant under our roof!

266
00:15:40,590 --> 00:15:41,550
Is it so, Rak?

267
00:15:45,570 --> 00:15:46,350
Whip him!

268
00:15:47,070 --> 00:15:48,470
Do not stop

269
00:15:48,710 --> 00:15:49,550
unless I command it!

270
00:15:49,950 --> 00:15:52,070
Stop! Harm him not!

271
00:15:53,030 --> 00:15:53,830
No!

272
00:15:54,030 --> 00:15:54,990
Unhand me!

273
00:15:55,710 --> 00:15:56,590
No!

274
00:15:56,990 --> 00:15:58,390
Father, stop!

275
00:15:59,670 --> 00:16:00,630
Stop!

276
00:16:04,870 --> 00:16:05,550
Hand that to me!

277
00:16:06,110 --> 00:16:07,030
I shall do it myself!

278
00:16:10,070 --> 00:16:10,870
No!

279
00:16:11,270 --> 00:16:12,430
Enough of this, Father!

280
00:16:17,530 --> 00:16:19,030
You are most ungrateful!

281
00:16:19,950 --> 00:16:22,070
I have nurtured you
since you were but a child,

282
00:16:22,630 --> 00:16:24,630
and yet you dare commit
such a sinful crime!

283
00:16:27,010 --> 00:16:28,390
Enough of this, Father.

284
00:16:28,790 --> 00:16:30,110
Harm him no more.

285
00:16:30,990 --> 00:16:32,030
If punishment must fall,

286
00:16:32,710 --> 00:16:34,350
let it be upon me alone.

287
00:16:35,050 --> 00:16:36,310
I beg you, release Saen.

288
00:16:39,230 --> 00:16:40,430
No!

289
00:16:44,750 --> 00:16:46,070
I beg you, stop!

290
00:16:48,670 --> 00:16:49,790
No more!

291
00:16:50,590 --> 00:16:51,710
No!

292
00:16:52,990 --> 00:16:54,150
Harm him no more!

293
00:16:56,870 --> 00:16:57,990
Lock him up

294
00:16:58,470 --> 00:16:59,790
and whip him.

295
00:17:00,630 --> 00:17:02,790
He shall see my son no more!

296
00:17:03,910 --> 00:17:05,510
Take my son upstairs,

297
00:17:06,070 --> 00:17:07,750
and fasten the door securely.

298
00:17:08,350 --> 00:17:09,750
Release him not

299
00:17:09,780 --> 00:17:12,470
until the day of his wedding!!

300
00:17:17,270 --> 00:17:18,110
No!

301
00:17:18,490 --> 00:17:19,510
Saen!

302
00:17:20,230 --> 00:17:21,350
Release me!

303
00:17:23,170 --> 00:17:24,030
Saen!

304
00:17:33,150 --> 00:17:34,150
Saen!!

305
00:17:43,430 --> 00:17:44,190
Why have you come?

306
00:17:47,070 --> 00:17:49,310
Are you the cause of all this turmoil?

307
00:17:50,110 --> 00:17:51,030
What more do you seek?

308
00:17:51,870 --> 00:17:53,230
You lay all evil deeds

309
00:17:53,570 --> 00:17:55,190
upon me.

310
00:17:56,470 --> 00:17:58,030
When, pray, was I to know

311
00:17:58,430 --> 00:18:00,750
that you and Master Rak
would commit such an affair?

312
00:18:10,350 --> 00:18:11,030
Master Rak...

313
00:18:11,670 --> 00:18:12,750
How fares he now?

314
00:18:17,170 --> 00:18:18,150
I know not.

315
00:18:18,990 --> 00:18:19,600
He may well be dead.

316
00:18:19,630 --> 00:18:20,470
Tan!

317
00:18:23,870 --> 00:18:25,950
He would not do such a thing
to his own son.

318
00:18:30,830 --> 00:18:31,710
Yet still,

319
00:18:32,830 --> 00:18:33,630
Master Rak

320
00:18:34,310 --> 00:18:35,590
is my life.

321
00:18:38,950 --> 00:18:39,990
Very well.

322
00:18:40,590 --> 00:18:42,950
You deem him master of your life.

323
00:18:44,390 --> 00:18:45,550
What of him?

324
00:18:46,130 --> 00:18:47,750
Could he ever defend you?

325
00:18:48,510 --> 00:18:49,870
For he chose his father,

326
00:18:50,630 --> 00:18:51,470
honor,

327
00:18:52,330 --> 00:18:53,430
and fortune.

328
00:18:54,590 --> 00:18:55,910
A son of noble blood,

329
00:18:56,150 --> 00:18:57,910
he pays no mind to servants such as us.

330
00:19:03,430 --> 00:19:04,230
Saen,

331
00:19:04,670 --> 00:19:05,870
shall I help you flee?

332
00:19:38,620 --> 00:19:39,400
Master Rak,

333
00:19:44,460 --> 00:19:46,040
will you not eat?

334
00:19:49,080 --> 00:19:50,840
You must surely take great delight in this.

335
00:19:55,440 --> 00:19:56,480
I swear,

336
00:19:57,380 --> 00:19:58,400
I knew nothing of this.

337
00:20:00,520 --> 00:20:01,620
Is it so?

338
00:20:02,550 --> 00:20:04,600
Then, you have come to mock me?

339
00:20:06,160 --> 00:20:08,020
I came here not to mock.

340
00:20:09,040 --> 00:20:10,200
I came to lend my aid.

341
00:20:11,580 --> 00:20:12,480
Why is that?

342
00:20:14,040 --> 00:20:15,200
You despise me.

343
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:17,000
That may be so,

344
00:20:18,200 --> 00:20:19,800
yet I know
what transpired at the apothecary.

345
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:27,840
Physician,

346
00:20:31,480 --> 00:20:33,580
I pray you, cure that man's mother.

347
00:20:42,040 --> 00:20:44,200
You owe him his due of gratitude,
mark me!

348
00:20:48,160 --> 00:20:49,360
Your mother lives,

349
00:20:50,900 --> 00:20:52,560
for he provided her with medicine.

350
00:20:56,240 --> 00:20:58,600
He even entrusted you to be an understudy.

351
00:21:02,520 --> 00:21:04,080
Master Rak, pray believe me.

352
00:21:04,820 --> 00:21:05,840
I mean no ill.

353
00:21:10,600 --> 00:21:11,840
How shall you aid me?

354
00:21:14,620 --> 00:21:16,120
I shall aid you and Saen

355
00:21:17,140 --> 00:21:18,440
in fleeing this place.

356
00:21:21,840 --> 00:21:22,880
We have no honor,

357
00:21:23,640 --> 00:21:24,920
yet we can still dance.

358
00:21:27,280 --> 00:21:29,760
Better that than to leave Master Rak
in a living death.

359
00:22:15,180 --> 00:22:16,850
The servants should be asleep at this hour,

360
00:22:16,880 --> 00:22:18,490
for they must rise early
on account of the wedding tomorrow.

361
00:22:18,520 --> 00:22:19,660
Now is a fitting hour to flee.

362
00:22:20,640 --> 00:22:21,320
Indeed.

363
00:22:21,520 --> 00:22:23,120
Beside that gate stands a wagon.

364
00:22:23,480 --> 00:22:25,160
I shall have it loosed when the time comes.

365
00:22:25,480 --> 00:22:26,810
The guards shall give chase.

366
00:22:26,840 --> 00:22:27,520
Very well.

367
00:22:27,680 --> 00:22:29,000
I arranged it with Choy,

368
00:22:29,120 --> 00:22:30,490
a servant at Miss Vila's residence

369
00:22:30,520 --> 00:22:32,010
who was sent to prepare the wedding,

370
00:22:32,040 --> 00:22:33,410
to delay the matter on that side.

371
00:22:33,440 --> 00:22:35,090
Are you certain we have not been seen?

372
00:22:35,120 --> 00:22:35,920
Most certainly.

373
00:22:36,120 --> 00:22:37,600
Very well. Let us away.

374
00:22:45,320 --> 00:22:46,040
Saen!

375
00:22:47,360 --> 00:22:48,080
This way.

376
00:22:59,260 --> 00:23:01,000
I thought I should see you no more.

377
00:23:04,200 --> 00:23:05,480
As did I.

378
00:23:07,520 --> 00:23:08,680
Let us make haste to the boat

379
00:23:08,920 --> 00:23:10,100
before we are seen.

380
00:23:22,360 --> 00:23:23,280
Rak!

381
00:23:32,560 --> 00:23:33,320
Tan!

382
00:23:35,400 --> 00:23:36,360
What is this?

383
00:23:36,640 --> 00:23:37,840
I have done you no betrayal.

384
00:23:38,080 --> 00:23:39,080
Indeed, you have.

385
00:23:40,460 --> 00:23:41,600
You have betrayed me.

386
00:23:43,640 --> 00:23:45,400
Never again shall you dance Khon.

387
00:23:46,880 --> 00:23:48,120
Not worthy are you.

388
00:23:48,720 --> 00:23:49,820
Is it because

389
00:23:50,460 --> 00:23:52,460
I lack the cruel heart to see one die?

390
00:23:53,520 --> 00:23:54,720
Or is it because

391
00:23:55,160 --> 00:23:57,040
I lack the wretched heart

392
00:23:57,340 --> 00:23:58,680
to part the one I love

393
00:23:59,580 --> 00:24:01,210
from his beloved?

394
00:24:01,240 --> 00:24:02,760
Dare you taunt me so?!

395
00:24:07,200 --> 00:24:08,400
What wrong have I committed?

396
00:24:10,880 --> 00:24:12,960
I am a dutiful daughter unto my father.

397
00:24:15,320 --> 00:24:17,320
I shall wed whomever my father appoints me.

398
00:24:19,400 --> 00:24:20,480
Yet the groom

399
00:24:21,520 --> 00:24:23,280
makes off with a male servant.

400
00:24:27,320 --> 00:24:28,240
This scandal

401
00:24:29,740 --> 00:24:31,880
shall leave a lasting blemish upon my life.

402
00:24:34,420 --> 00:24:35,680
What fault have I committed?

403
00:24:40,200 --> 00:24:41,360
I told them

404
00:24:43,900 --> 00:24:46,140
that I wish not to wed him who loves me not,

405
00:24:47,140 --> 00:24:48,840
yet they forced me into this union.

406
00:24:50,880 --> 00:24:52,400
My duty as a daughter

407
00:24:54,420 --> 00:24:56,560
is to bring no shame upon my father.

408
00:24:59,020 --> 00:25:00,160
Tomorrow,

409
00:25:01,560 --> 00:25:03,360
I shall appear a fool at my own wedding.

410
00:25:05,980 --> 00:25:08,360
Who shall ease
this burden of shame upon me?

411
00:25:19,500 --> 00:25:20,400
Forgive me.

412
00:25:28,280 --> 00:25:29,640
Yet no choice have I.

413
00:25:34,180 --> 00:25:35,880
Indeed, you do.

414
00:25:38,260 --> 00:25:40,260
Yet you chose this path,

415
00:25:43,140 --> 00:25:44,200
for you

416
00:25:45,960 --> 00:25:47,640
see no soul...

417
00:25:48,620 --> 00:25:50,160
except this man.

418
00:26:00,480 --> 00:26:02,040
Will you grant me my freedom?

419
00:26:05,560 --> 00:26:06,640
No.

420
00:26:10,400 --> 00:26:11,200
All of you,

421
00:26:12,160 --> 00:26:13,520
return Rak to his manor!

422
00:26:14,040 --> 00:26:14,720
No!

423
00:26:17,020 --> 00:26:17,760
Master Rak.

424
00:26:18,580 --> 00:26:19,050
No.

425
00:26:19,080 --> 00:26:20,120
Stop!

426
00:26:20,360 --> 00:26:21,450
- What is it you do?
- No!

427
00:26:21,480 --> 00:26:22,210
- Master Rak!
- Master Rak!!

428
00:26:22,240 --> 00:26:23,050
- No!
- Master Rak!

429
00:26:23,080 --> 00:26:23,430
Come.

430
00:26:23,460 --> 00:26:24,610
- Unhand him!
- Release me!

431
00:26:25,400 --> 00:26:26,040
Master Rak!

432
00:26:26,800 --> 00:26:27,720
Saen!

433
00:26:28,000 --> 00:26:28,600
Master Rak!

434
00:26:28,880 --> 00:26:29,600
Saen!

435
00:26:30,920 --> 00:26:31,800
Master Rak!!
